column2: ggplot(data, aes(x = ejection_fraction )) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 5, colour =  "white", fill = "blue", alpha = 0.7) + labs(title = "Histogram of Ejection Fraction") + geom_density(eval(bquote(aes(y=..count..*5))),colour="black") + geom_vline(xintercept = 40, linetype = "dashed") + annotate("text", x = 20, y = 60, label = "Abnormal") + annotate("text", x = 55, y = 60, label = "Normal")
